State of North Carolina
v.
Kalvin Michael Smith No. 85P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 James E. Coleman, Jr., Attorney, for Smith, Kalvin Michael. Danielle Marquis Elder, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mary Carla Babb, Assistant Attorney General, James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 11th of March 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Forsyth County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
